item.title: By: Suzi
item.dc:creator: Suzi
item.description: Although I'm terrified to put oil in my hair, you've given me a new beauty mantra: "You might really fuck it up the first time, but probably not the 5th or 6th time." Love it. I will now be saying this to myself every time I attempt to do winged eyeliner.
item.content:encoded: Although I’m terrified to put oil in my hair, you’ve given me a new beauty mantra: “You might really fuck it up the first time, but probably not the 5th or 6th time.” Love it. I will now be saying this to myself every time I attempt to do winged eyeliner.
